{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Geolocation","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation\"><code>Geolocation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/clearWatch\"><code>clearWatch()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/getCurrentPosition\"><code>getCurrentPosition()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/watchPosition\"><code>watchPosition()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>Geolocation</strong></code>&nbsp;接口是一个用来获取设备地理位置的可编程的对象，它可以让 Web 内容访问到设备的地理位置，这将允许 Web 应用基于用户的地理位置提供定制的信息。说实话：其实<code><strong>Geolocation</strong></code>&nbsp;就是用来获取到当前设备的经纬度（位置）</p>\n\n<p>带有此接口的对象可以用由 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a>实现的属性<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/geolocation\"><code>NavigatorGeolocation.geolocation</code></a> 来获得。 &nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>注意：</strong>出于安全考虑，当一个 Web 页尝试获取地理位置信息时，会请求用户批准地理位置访问权限。要知道每个浏览器都有自己请求用户批准该权限的策略和方法。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><code>Geolocation</code>&nbsp;接口不实现，也不继承任何属性。</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><em><code>Geolocation</code></em>&nbsp;<em>接口不继承任何方法。</em></em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"geolocation.getcurrentposition\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/getCurrentPosition\"><code>Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>确定设备的位置并返回一个携带位置信息的<em>&nbsp;</em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition\"><code>Position</code></a> 对象。</dd>\n <dt id=\"geolocation.watchposition\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/watchPosition\"><code>Geolocation.watchPosition()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>注册一个位置改变监听器，每当设备位置改变时，返回一个 <code>long</code> 类型的该监听器的 ID 值。</dd>\n <dt id=\"geolocation.clearwatch\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/clearWatch\"><code>Geolocation.clearWatch()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>取消由&nbsp;<code>watchPosition() 注册的位置监听器。</code></dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/geolocation-api/#geolocation_interface","title":"Geolocation API"}],"query":"api.Geolocation"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Geolocation","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation_API\" title=\"/en-US/docs/WebAPI/Using_geolocation\">使用地理位置定位</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"Geolocation 接口是一个用来获取设备地理位置的可编程的对象，它可以让 Web 内容访问到设备的地理位置，这将允许 Web 应用基于用户的地理位置提供定制的信息。说实话：其实Geolocation 就是用来获取到当前设备的经纬度（位置）","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Geolocalización","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/geolocation","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/geolocation/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation","title":"Geolocation"}],"pageTitle":"Geolocation - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}